  "detailed_description": "Returning home after a work trip Bion finds that his family is gone and the city is flooded by bloodthirsty creatures that someday used to be people. The hero goes on a search of his family, visiting the most various places and at the same time trying to survive.<br><br>Hope of Bion is an adventure game with a lean towards story and atmosphere. Visit different locations, examine the objects of environment and fight enemies using weapons of melee and ranged combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/1624206d594adcd26f9440c5861d30fd.poster.avif?t=1756363189\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/1624206d594adcd26f9440c5861d30fd.webm?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/1624206d594adcd26f9440c5861d30fd.mp4?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 story campaigns with a total length of 4-5 hours;<br></li><li>interesting and atmospheric adventures with elements of action, puzzles, platforming and horror;<br></li><li>different levels, both in terms of location and tasks;<br></li><li>interesting and funny mini-games;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/a67c1ae4980bc713dcc22bc9b893b8d6.poster.avif?t=1756363189\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/a67c1ae4980bc713dcc22bc9b893b8d6.webm?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/a67c1ae4980bc713dcc22bc9b893b8d6.mp4?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>ability to interact with the objects of environment and to communicate with the other survivors;<br></li><li>defend yourself using a baseball bat or a firearm, but remember that ammunition is not endless;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/84409c7dca44b357056fa64efadaf510.poster.avif?t=1756363189\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/84409c7dca44b357056fa64efadaf510.webm?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/84409c7dca44b357056fa64efadaf510.mp4?t=1756363189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>enemies need only one bite to kill the hero;<br></li><li>the game is developed by one person.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526210/extras/982978fb6a96067c6a7cfa1a0e3c18e7.avif?t=1756363189\" width=349 height=296 /></span>",
